<!--
  Full-colour 2D cyclist avatar shown as the live-location marker. Drawn as a
  clean 3rd-person / top-down rider pointing "up" (north before any rotation):
  two slim wheels front & back, a narrow frame, the handlebar with gripping
  hands, a compact rider (helmet, shoulders, arms reaching forward, legs reaching
  back to the pedals). Rendered as an upright billboard, so it reads as a clear
  top-down cyclist even on the tilted 3D navigation map.
-->
